tournament final against Georgia Tech. 
</P>
<P>
Ronnie Battle scored 21 points for Auburn (6-2), which never got closer than 12 
points in the second half. 
</P>
<P>
Georgia Tech 95, Tulane 83 -- Malcolm Mackey scored 26 points and Kenny 
