buzzer and Ocean View's rally fell short in the second round. Ryan Rauch scored 
20 for Woodbridge, which led, 29-21, at the half. Ryan Martin missed the game 
with a back injury he suffered in a first-round game Wednesday. Bryan Knox 
scored 14 for Ocean View (5-6). 
</P>
