Genevieve at 4 p.m. today. 
</P>
<P>
In the Torrance District tournament: 
</P>
<P>
Leuzinger 85, Rancho Alamitos 60 -- Matt Roberts scored 13 points for Rancho 
Alamitos in a semifinal. 
