difference, officials said, because Bush believes a delay would increase 
American casualties. Above, U.S. soldiers Eddie Ramos, left, and David Gibbs 
used bandannas to shield themselves against a sandstorm in Saudi Arabia. 
Associated Press; Photo, (Southland Edition) President Bush talks with 
reporters on arrival at White House. United Press International 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
