<TEXT>
<P>
" I resolve to fight to keep a regional airport out of southern Orange County 
and offshore oil drilling rigs off our coastline. I resolve to successfully 
push the adoption of an ordinance limiting terms on the Dana Point City Council 
to two consecutive terms and the adoption of an ordinance limiting campaign 
contributions for Dana Point City Council races. I will try to figure out a way 
we can finish our City Council meetings by 11 p.m. and, finally, to enjoy 
public service while not taking the title honorable too seriously. 
</P>
