<HEADLINE>
<P>
O.C. STOCK WATCH 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Of the 102 largest publicly traded companies in Orange County, 24 gained value 
Thursday, 31 lost and 47 remained unchanged for the day. 
</P>
